HEADWORD: Molech
<hw>Mo"lech</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[Heb.
<ets>molek</ets> king.]</ety> <fld>(Script.)</fld> <def>The fire god of
the Ammonites, to whom human sacrifices were offered; Moloch.</def>
